4Geeks Academy offers a 16-week Data Science and Machine Learning course. The course covers Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics. Students will learn to create predictive models using Python libraries such as Pandas and Numpy, and explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. The course also includes real-life case studies, industry-standard tools, and the opportunity to develop AI projects from development to deployment and maintenance. No previous experience is required, and the course is available in English and Spanish. Classes are held three times a week with a maximum class size of 12 people. Upon completion, students receive a recognized certificate. For more information, visit the website: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop